	* Gui/Dialogs/CombineConfiguration/CombineStartupPanel.cs:
	Use new StartupEntry property instead of SingleStartProjectName.
	* Gui/Pads/ProjectPad/ProjectFileNodeBuilder.cs: Use the correct
	menu path.
